WEBVTT

00:00:17.830 --> 00:00:18.690 line:80%
Your Lordship,

00:00:19.920 --> 00:00:22.760 line:80%
two female military medics
on the grain transport crew

00:00:22.760 --> 00:00:24.420 line:80%
request an audience with you.

00:00:27.670 --> 00:00:29.070 line:80%
Female military medics?

00:00:32.640 --> 00:00:33.590 line:80%
Bring them in.

00:00:35.080 --> 00:00:36.880 line:80%
Brace yourself, Your Lordship.

00:00:54.590 --> 00:00:56.680 line:80%
I'm temporarily acting as
a royal physician

00:00:56.680 --> 00:00:59.400 line:80%
and comforting the army
on behalf of His Majesty.

00:00:59.400 --> 00:01:02.290 line:80%
During the journey, I heard you were
trapped in a mountain near Wu River.

00:01:02.290 --> 00:01:03.690 line:80%
So I decided to come here.

00:01:03.840 --> 00:01:07.040 line:80%
You snuck out
during an incense-offering ritual, right?

00:01:08.030 --> 00:01:09.540 line:80%
This is a battlefield,

00:01:09.610 --> 00:01:10.870 line:80%
not your playground.

00:01:10.870 --> 00:01:11.720 line:80%
Don't be a clever clogs again,

00:01:11.720 --> 00:01:13.560 line:80%
or there will be catastrophic outcomes.

00:01:13.560 --> 00:01:14.750 line:80%
Anyway,

00:01:15.230 --> 00:01:17.360 line:80%
I'm a blessed noble lady.

00:01:18.280 --> 00:01:20.510 line:80%
Plus,
the pig butcher squad was by my side.

00:01:20.510 --> 00:01:21.920 line:80%
They helped me break the siege

00:01:21.920 --> 00:01:22.980 line:80%
and escape danger.

00:01:23.640 --> 00:01:25.700 line:80%
There are people on the cliff! Shoot!

00:01:26.030 --> 00:01:27.470 line:80%
Oh no, they found us.

00:01:28.280 --> 00:01:28.940 line:80%
Take cover!

00:01:36.230 --> 00:01:37.230 line:80%
Give me your hand.

00:01:49.710 --> 00:01:51.290 line:80%
You were just lucky enough

00:01:51.380 --> 00:01:52.080 line:80%
to get

00:01:52.080 --> 00:01:53.920 line:80%
within our archers' range.

00:01:55.029 --> 00:01:56.800 line:80%
If you had been caught
by Shi Yue and his men,

00:01:56.800 --> 00:01:58.670 line:80%
do you know what would've happened to you?

00:01:58.670 --> 00:02:00.130 line:80%
At best, sexual assaults.

00:02:00.150 --> 00:02:01.680 line:80%
At worst, a gruesome death.

00:02:08.920 --> 00:02:10.830 line:80%
I did act rashly

00:02:10.990 --> 00:02:12.790 line:80%
and never considered the risks.

00:02:13.520 --> 00:02:14.800 line:80%
Punish me

00:02:15.560 --> 00:02:16.360 line:80%
as you please.

00:02:22.640 --> 00:02:23.290 line:80%
Your Lordship,

00:02:23.290 --> 00:02:24.270 line:80%
Counselor is asking for a meeting

00:02:24.270 --> 00:02:26.129 line:80%
with you about military affairs.

00:02:27.270 --> 00:02:28.110 line:80%
"Counselor"?

00:02:29.270 --> 00:02:33.430 line:80%
Does it refer to... Headmaster Gongsun?

00:02:40.120 --> 00:02:42.980 line:80%
As it turns out,
despite life-threatening danger,

00:02:43.360 --> 00:02:45.140 line:80%
Your Highness came here

00:02:45.390 --> 00:02:47.950 line:80%
for more than a simple visit.

00:02:48.990 --> 00:02:51.080 line:80%
Your Lordship is fighting for the people.

00:02:51.080 --> 00:02:52.430 line:80%
As the Princess Royal,

00:02:52.920 --> 00:02:54.450 line:80%
I feel obligated to check on

00:02:54.800 --> 00:02:55.990 line:80%
Your Lordship's safety.

00:02:55.990 --> 00:02:57.060 line:80%
In that case,

00:02:57.430 --> 00:02:58.360 line:80%
I will arrange

00:02:58.890 --> 00:03:01.420 line:80%
a separate tent for you, Physician,

00:03:01.950 --> 00:03:04.500 line:80%
in gratitude for His Majesty's kindness.

00:03:08.430 --> 00:03:09.110 line:80%
Xie Qi,

00:03:09.600 --> 00:03:10.990 line:80%
show these royal physicians out.

00:03:10.990 --> 00:03:11.390 line:80%
Yes.

00:03:12.550 --> 00:03:15.080 line:80%
Thanks for such hospitality,
Your Lordship.

00:03:17.670 --> 00:03:18.360 line:80%
Please.

00:03:22.670 --> 00:03:23.879 line:80%
Have a few well-mannered soldiers

00:03:23.879 --> 00:03:25.270 line:80%
wait on the Princess Royal.

00:03:25.270 --> 00:03:27.670 line:80%
Keep those sloppy military ruffians away,

00:03:27.930 --> 00:03:29.200 line:80%
so they won't cause trouble

00:03:29.200 --> 00:03:30.530 line:80%
or offend the princess.

00:03:30.830 --> 00:03:31.960 line:80%
Yes, Your Lordship.

00:03:36.990 --> 00:03:38.920 line:80%
It was the pig butcher squad again.

00:05:05.070 --> 00:05:10.460 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:05:10.490 --> 00:05:13.060 line:80%
[Episode 24]

00:05:16.750 --> 00:05:17.840 line:80%
It smells so good.

00:05:19.430 --> 00:05:22.430 line:80%
We were running out of food.
Finally, there's something to eat today.

00:05:22.430 --> 00:05:24.960 line:80%
I heard there was a grain delivery
last night.

00:05:25.310 --> 00:05:28.330 line:80%
Yes. We finally get to fill our stomaches.

00:05:28.750 --> 00:05:30.600 line:80%
Sir, do you know Yan Zheng?

00:05:30.600 --> 00:05:31.630 line:80%
No.

00:05:34.630 --> 00:05:37.520 line:80%
-Sir, do you know Yan Zheng?
-No.

00:05:37.990 --> 00:05:39.550 line:80%
Sir, do you know Yan Zheng?

00:05:39.550 --> 00:05:40.160 line:80%
No, I don't.

00:05:40.160 --> 00:05:41.750 line:80%
Sir, do you know Yan Zheng?

00:05:42.040 --> 00:05:43.190 line:80%
No.

00:05:44.070 --> 00:05:45.270 line:80%
Do you know Yan Zheng?

00:05:45.430 --> 00:05:46.200 line:80%
No.

00:05:47.070 --> 00:05:47.840 line:80%
Gentlemen,

00:05:47.959 --> 00:05:49.310 line:80%
do you know Yan Zheng?

00:05:49.310 --> 00:05:50.550 line:80%
He's a soldier from Lin'an.

00:05:50.550 --> 00:05:51.480 line:80%
Never heard of him.

00:05:51.480 --> 00:05:52.540 line:80%
Is he your husband?

00:05:55.670 --> 00:05:56.870 line:80%
He's about this tall.

00:05:58.550 --> 00:06:01.070 line:80%
He has large almond-shaped eyes.

00:06:01.630 --> 00:06:03.690 line:80%
There's a mole right here on his nose.

00:06:04.120 --> 00:06:06.400 line:80%
He looks a bit intimidating
when he's not smiling.

00:06:06.400 --> 00:06:08.060 line:80%
But when he is, he seems silly.

00:06:08.230 --> 00:06:09.230 line:80%
He's from Lin'an.

00:06:09.960 --> 00:06:11.490 line:80%
I haven't seen this person.

00:06:11.840 --> 00:06:13.750 line:80%
A troop consists of
nearly one thousand men.

00:06:13.750 --> 00:06:15.210 line:80%
There's a lot of movement.

00:06:15.400 --> 00:06:16.990 line:80%
We can't possibly know everyone.

00:06:16.990 --> 00:06:17.890 line:80%
That's right.

00:06:18.870 --> 00:06:19.720 line:80%
Thanks.

00:06:20.160 --> 00:06:21.180 line:80%
No problem.

00:06:24.720 --> 00:06:26.310 line:80%
There are three types of soldiers
in this area,

00:06:26.310 --> 00:06:27.800 line:80%
amounting to one thousand people.

00:06:27.800 --> 00:06:29.400 line:80%
How are you going to find him?

00:06:29.960 --> 00:06:32.230 line:80%
I saw the falcon delivering a message
down the mountain,

00:06:32.230 --> 00:06:33.990 line:80%
so I thought Yan Zheng was here.

00:06:34.720 --> 00:06:36.520 line:80%
That matrilocal husband of yours
is a mere foot soldier.

00:06:36.520 --> 00:06:37.470 line:80%
Even if someone saw him,

00:06:37.470 --> 00:06:38.870 line:80%
would they remember him?

00:06:47.780 --> 00:06:50.250 line:80%
[Xie]

00:07:01.160 --> 00:07:03.820 line:80%
Still thinking about
your matrilocal husband?

00:07:07.360 --> 00:07:08.360 line:80%
I'm wondering...

00:07:10.610 --> 00:07:12.280 line:80%
if he already died in battle.

00:07:18.990 --> 00:07:20.720 line:80%
It's late. I'm trying to sleep!

00:07:21.960 --> 00:07:23.600 line:80%
Which mountain are you from?

00:07:23.750 --> 00:07:24.720 line:80%
Go to sleep!

00:07:24.720 --> 00:07:25.280 line:80%
Fine, I will.

00:07:25.280 --> 00:07:26.120 line:80%
Why the rage?

00:07:27.750 --> 00:07:28.720 line:80%
Good thing you held me back,

00:07:28.720 --> 00:07:30.850 line:80%
or I would've dashed and beaten him up.

00:07:36.630 --> 00:07:38.690 line:80%
I've been wondering about one thing.

00:07:39.430 --> 00:07:40.480 line:80%
Previously, the few of us

00:07:40.480 --> 00:07:42.520 line:80%
went to your place
to collect debts, right?

00:07:42.520 --> 00:07:44.110 line:80%
I just couldn't figure out how we ended up

00:07:44.110 --> 00:07:45.600 line:80%
being beaten by that bunch of old folks,

00:07:45.600 --> 00:07:46.870 line:80%
including Mr. Zhao.

00:07:47.310 --> 00:07:48.630 line:80%
But then I understood.

00:07:48.630 --> 00:07:51.430 line:80%
You matrilocal husband
must have done something.

00:07:52.520 --> 00:07:53.520 line:80%
So,

00:07:53.520 --> 00:07:54.980 line:80%
don't you worry about him.

00:07:58.870 --> 00:08:00.130 line:80%
Still don't get it?

00:08:00.160 --> 00:08:01.190 line:80%
That is to say,

00:08:01.190 --> 00:08:03.750 line:80%
Mr. Yan is as good a fighter as you are.

00:08:05.190 --> 00:08:06.400 line:80%
You lot really deserved

00:08:06.400 --> 00:08:07.800 line:80%
to be beaten up last time.

00:08:09.690 --> 00:08:11.720 line:80%
Why call him Mr. Yan?

00:08:11.990 --> 00:08:12.920 line:80%
It sounds odd.

00:08:14.910 --> 00:08:16.190 line:80%
Frankly speaking,

00:08:16.190 --> 00:08:18.720 line:80%
her matrilocal husband
is quite impressive.

00:08:18.720 --> 00:08:20.600 line:80%
Aren't I, Manwu, an amazing man myself?

00:08:20.600 --> 00:08:22.460 line:80%
But even I would tremble with fear

00:08:23.360 --> 00:08:25.040 line:80%
when I look into his eyes.

00:08:25.550 --> 00:08:26.800 line:80%
Let alone "Mr. Yan"—

00:08:26.800 --> 00:08:28.530 line:80%
I'd call him "Lord" if I have to.

00:08:29.430 --> 00:08:31.290 line:80%
Just call him "Brother-in-Law."

00:08:31.950 --> 00:08:33.589 line:80%
We'll be family from now on.

00:08:34.400 --> 00:08:35.880 line:80%
Even Mandi calls me "Sister" now.

00:08:35.880 --> 00:08:36.880 line:80%
"Sister"?

00:08:37.120 --> 00:08:37.800 line:80%
Sister.

00:08:38.120 --> 00:08:38.760 line:80%
Sister.

00:08:39.800 --> 00:08:40.640 line:80%
Sister.

00:08:45.880 --> 00:08:46.590 line:80%
What?

00:08:47.640 --> 00:08:49.410 line:80%
You want to take advantage of me?

00:08:49.410 --> 00:08:50.160 line:80%
I'm telling you,

00:08:50.160 --> 00:08:52.290 line:80%
there's no way I'll call you "Sister."

00:08:52.470 --> 00:08:53.860 line:80%
But you did just now.

00:08:53.950 --> 00:08:54.760 line:80%
When?

00:08:54.760 --> 00:08:55.390 line:80%
Did I ever call her "Sister"?

00:08:55.390 --> 00:08:57.850 line:80%
-See? You just said it again.
-He did, right?

00:08:58.120 --> 00:08:58.830 line:80%
You brat...

00:08:58.830 --> 00:09:00.220 line:80%
Fancy a beating or what?

00:09:00.550 --> 00:09:02.360 line:80%
You're not a man of your word!

00:09:02.430 --> 00:09:04.290 line:80%
-Stop moving!
-I'm afraid of you.

00:09:04.430 --> 00:09:05.160 line:80%
Come here!

00:09:05.160 --> 00:09:07.430 line:80%
-Sister, he's about to hit me.
-Sister, he wants to hit me!

00:09:07.430 --> 00:09:09.070 line:80%
-Sister...
-You little brat,

00:09:09.070 --> 00:09:10.120 line:80%
this stool will teach you...

00:09:10.120 --> 00:09:10.470 line:80%
Hey.

00:09:10.470 --> 00:09:11.920 line:80%
I've already told you to stop

00:09:11.920 --> 00:09:12.780 line:80%
making noises.

00:09:13.190 --> 00:09:14.520 line:80%
What now? How about we rock you to sleep?

00:09:14.520 --> 00:09:15.720 line:80%
You can't sleep, huh?

00:09:15.830 --> 00:09:16.960 line:80%
Come on, let me help.

00:09:17.830 --> 00:09:19.520 line:80%
-Come on.
-You want some sleep, huh?

00:09:19.520 --> 00:09:21.240 line:80%
Sir, I was wrong!

00:09:21.240 --> 00:09:22.430 line:80%
Sir. Sir...

00:09:22.430 --> 00:09:23.640 line:80%
Sir,

00:09:23.640 --> 00:09:24.650 line:80%
I won't sleep. I won't.

00:09:24.650 --> 00:09:25.850 line:80%
Please don't hurt me!

00:10:35.280 --> 00:10:36.740 line:80%
Your Lordship is injured.

00:10:36.800 --> 00:10:37.800 line:80%
Just let us patrol

00:10:37.820 --> 00:10:39.070 line:80%
the camp instead.

00:10:41.280 --> 00:10:41.880 line:80%
Alright.

00:10:42.720 --> 00:10:43.650 line:80%
Off you go, then.

00:11:01.680 --> 00:11:11.760 line:80%
♪ In gold-thread dress,
with moth or willow ornaments ♪

00:11:12.470 --> 00:11:22.190 line:80%
♪ Giggling, she melts into the throng
with trails of scents ♪

00:11:23.180 --> 00:11:27.700 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:11:27.720 --> 00:11:32.800 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:11:33.360 --> 00:11:35.560 line:80%
♪ When all at once I turn my head ♪

00:11:35.870 --> 00:11:40.500 line:80%
♪ I find her there ♪

00:11:42.160 --> 00:11:51.650 line:80%
♪ Where lantern light is dimly shed ♪

00:12:29.150 --> 00:12:35.530 line:80%
[Xie]

00:12:34.920 --> 00:12:35.520 line:80%
Step back.

00:12:36.590 --> 00:12:37.880 line:80%
By His Lordship's order,

00:12:37.880 --> 00:12:40.350 line:80%
you must stay in your tent,
Royal Physician.

00:12:41.240 --> 00:12:44.570 line:80%
I assume there are many
wounded soldiers in the camp, right?

00:12:45.310 --> 00:12:46.400 line:80%
Indeed, quite a few.

00:12:46.400 --> 00:12:47.950 line:80%
But they're all attended to.

00:12:47.950 --> 00:12:49.880 line:80%
No need to worry, Royal Physician.

00:12:50.160 --> 00:12:51.470 line:80%
There is clearly a shortage
of physicians and medicine.

00:12:51.470 --> 00:12:53.270 line:80%
Why not let me treat the wounded?

00:12:54.070 --> 00:12:55.550 line:80%
They're all military roughnecks

00:12:55.550 --> 00:12:57.160 line:80%
who tend to make rude remarks.

00:12:57.160 --> 00:12:58.590 line:80%
I'd hate for them to offend you.

00:12:58.590 --> 00:12:59.950 line:80%
Are unnecessary formalities

00:12:59.950 --> 00:13:01.810 line:80%
more important than human lives?

00:13:01.940 --> 00:13:04.940 line:80%
Can you bear to watch
your fellow military men suffer?

00:13:30.080 --> 00:13:31.040 line:80%
As I told you,

00:13:31.070 --> 00:13:32.430 line:80%
this is no place for you.

00:13:32.550 --> 00:13:34.750 line:80%
You're better off resting in your tent.

00:13:42.160 --> 00:13:43.780 line:80%
Your broken bone was set incorrectly.

00:13:43.780 --> 00:13:45.430 line:80%
It needs re-breaking and resetting.

00:13:45.430 --> 00:13:46.590 line:80%
What?

00:13:46.870 --> 00:13:48.040 line:80%
I just got it bandaged up.

00:13:48.040 --> 00:13:50.240 line:80%
Why should I listen to you
and break the bone again?

00:13:50.240 --> 00:13:52.040 line:80%
You haven't even touched my leg.

00:13:52.160 --> 00:13:54.240 line:80%
-Is a glance enough to make a diagnosis?
-How dare you!

00:13:54.240 --> 00:13:55.470 line:80%
Young lady, you...

00:13:55.880 --> 00:13:57.080 line:80%
You're talking to...

00:13:57.950 --> 00:13:59.040 line:80%
a royal physician.

00:13:59.070 --> 00:14:00.280 line:80%
Show some respect.

00:14:00.590 --> 00:14:01.550 line:80%
Got it,

00:14:01.800 --> 00:14:02.760 line:80%
General Wu.

00:14:03.040 --> 00:14:05.000 line:80%
Actually, my leg is almost healed.

00:14:05.280 --> 00:14:06.000 line:80%
Look.

00:14:06.430 --> 00:14:07.280 line:80%
Watch me.

00:14:07.800 --> 00:14:09.800 line:80%
I can even walk now. See?

00:14:09.830 --> 00:14:11.190 line:80%
There's no need to break my bone
and reset it.

00:14:11.190 --> 00:14:12.920 line:80%
-It'll hurt a lot.
-Don't move.

00:14:13.120 --> 00:14:14.250 line:80%
I'm perfectly well.

00:14:14.950 --> 00:14:15.470 line:80%
Be seated.

00:14:15.470 --> 00:14:16.030 line:80%
Fine.

00:14:16.920 --> 00:14:17.830 line:80%
Get some rest.

00:14:18.040 --> 00:14:18.760 line:80%
Sure.

00:14:18.790 --> 00:14:20.010 line:80%
Got it.

00:14:21.400 --> 00:14:22.190 line:80%
Take a rest.

00:14:32.030 --> 00:14:34.890 line:80%
This salve treats the symptoms,
not the root cause.

00:14:41.430 --> 00:14:42.800 line:80%
Your injury will quickly heal

00:14:42.800 --> 00:14:44.520 line:80%
after the rotten flesh is scraped,

00:14:44.520 --> 00:14:46.160 line:80%
the Regeneration Powder is applied
externally,

00:14:46.160 --> 00:14:47.890 line:80%
and the Cleansing Soup is taken

00:14:47.950 --> 00:14:48.950 line:80%
internally.

00:14:49.800 --> 00:14:51.660 line:80%
What is the Regeneration Powder?

00:14:51.670 --> 00:14:53.040 line:80%
It's mainly made of ganoderma,

00:14:53.040 --> 00:14:54.590 line:80%
and some common herbs.

00:14:54.610 --> 00:14:55.740 line:80%
Ganoderma?

00:14:55.920 --> 00:14:57.020 line:80%
Royal Physician,

00:14:57.160 --> 00:14:59.330 line:80%
do we also need

00:14:59.470 --> 00:15:00.590 line:80%
some ginseng?

00:15:05.190 --> 00:15:05.950 line:80%
No.

00:15:06.470 --> 00:15:07.550 line:80%
Ginseng causes internal heat.

00:15:07.550 --> 00:15:08.880 line:80%
It's not a good fit here.

00:15:13.400 --> 00:15:14.400 line:80%
Royal Physician,

00:15:15.280 --> 00:15:16.550 line:80%
I'm not sure...

00:15:16.710 --> 00:15:18.640 line:80%
if I can be cured by ganoderma.

00:15:18.950 --> 00:15:21.820 line:80%
But it surely values more than my life.

00:15:21.950 --> 00:15:24.320 line:80%
Your life is too worthless to be saved
by ganoderma.

00:15:24.320 --> 00:15:25.780 line:80%
A mere tree branch will do.

00:15:26.350 --> 00:15:28.640 line:80%
How rude of you. Stop with this impudence!

00:15:28.640 --> 00:15:29.400 line:80%
Enough!

00:15:29.920 --> 00:15:30.920 line:80%
Stop laughing, all of you.

00:15:30.920 --> 00:15:32.260 line:80%
Don't your wounds hurt anymore?

00:15:32.260 --> 00:15:32.920 line:80%
Dismissed!

00:15:34.590 --> 00:15:35.520 line:80%
The wounds hurt.

00:15:35.610 --> 00:15:37.300 line:80%
Of course the wounds hurt.

00:15:38.040 --> 00:15:39.190 line:80%
Are there no such

00:15:39.470 --> 00:15:41.730 line:80%
common medicines at this military camp?

00:15:43.070 --> 00:15:45.310 line:80%
You've lived in the palace for too long,
so you wouldn't know.

00:15:45.310 --> 00:15:46.640 line:80%
It's already hard to get

00:15:46.710 --> 00:15:49.160 line:80%
these regular herbs and remedies
in the army.

00:15:49.160 --> 00:15:51.690 line:80%
Precious medicinal materials are luxuries.

00:16:07.990 --> 00:16:09.710 line:80%
You were being so rude just now.

00:16:09.710 --> 00:16:11.770 line:80%
That was a royal physician after all.

00:16:11.920 --> 00:16:12.800 line:80%
General Wu,

00:16:12.800 --> 00:16:15.950 line:80%
if we die on the battlefield, at least
our families will receive pensions.

00:16:15.950 --> 00:16:19.040 line:80%
But if we die at the hands
of that female royal physician,

00:16:19.040 --> 00:16:20.520 line:80%
it will be a huge waste.

00:16:20.800 --> 00:16:21.870 line:80%
Exactly.

00:16:24.610 --> 00:16:27.250 line:80%
[Marquis of Wu'an]

00:16:55.920 --> 00:16:57.240 line:80%
Yan Zheng is in fact

00:16:57.310 --> 00:16:58.670 line:80%
quite a good fighter.

00:16:59.070 --> 00:17:00.950 line:80%
He can't be as severely injured
as they are.

00:17:00.950 --> 00:17:03.040 line:80%
Come on, look at these wounded soldiers.

00:17:03.040 --> 00:17:04.460 line:80%
They're all muscular and strong.

00:17:04.460 --> 00:17:06.070 line:80%
Sturdier than your husband, right?

00:17:06.070 --> 00:17:08.040 line:80%
But aren't they still badly injured now?

00:17:08.040 --> 00:17:08.760 line:80%
Listen,

00:17:08.760 --> 00:17:12.020 line:80%
soldiers lose a limb or two
on the battlefield. It happens.

00:17:12.430 --> 00:17:13.510 line:80%
Forget what I said.

00:17:13.830 --> 00:17:15.440 line:80%
Gods and deities, do bless her husband.

00:17:15.440 --> 00:17:16.200 line:80%
Bless us, too.

00:17:16.200 --> 00:17:18.960 line:80%
I'll still provide for him
even if he loses a limb or two.

00:17:18.960 --> 00:17:21.110 line:80%
He was a badly injured refugee
from Chongzhou

00:17:21.110 --> 00:17:22.240 line:80%
when I first met him.

00:17:22.280 --> 00:17:23.909 line:80%
But he recovered at last under my care.

00:17:23.909 --> 00:17:25.240 line:80%
How are you recovering?

00:17:30.280 --> 00:17:31.480 line:80%
Mrs. Fan?

00:17:31.590 --> 00:17:32.760 line:80%
Mr. Sun?

00:17:34.440 --> 00:17:35.750 line:80%
Why are you here?

00:17:37.000 --> 00:17:38.730 line:80%
The pig butcher squad?

00:17:39.070 --> 00:17:40.590 line:80%
What are you doing here?

00:17:42.550 --> 00:17:44.830 line:80%
You're here looking for Changning, right?

00:17:44.830 --> 00:17:46.140 line:80%
Is Changning here?

00:17:47.350 --> 00:17:48.150 line:80%
Yes, she is.

00:17:48.310 --> 00:17:50.000 line:80%
Not in this tent. Come with me.

00:18:08.040 --> 00:18:09.880 line:80%
Sister.

00:18:26.350 --> 00:18:27.550 line:80%
Changning...

00:18:32.380 --> 00:18:34.200 line:80%
Come on, let me see you.

00:18:37.480 --> 00:18:39.150 line:80%
I finally found you.

00:18:40.310 --> 00:18:41.570 line:80%
Sister,

00:18:41.960 --> 00:18:43.880 line:80%
you finally came for me.

00:18:44.590 --> 00:18:46.590 line:80%
I missed you so much.

00:18:49.070 --> 00:18:52.260 line:80%
That little villain came to Lin'an
and killed.

00:18:55.440 --> 00:18:57.280 line:80%
Slow down. No rush.

00:18:57.280 --> 00:18:58.810 line:80%
And Bao'er...

00:18:58.960 --> 00:19:02.440 line:80%
Fairy Sister refused to be taken away
by that big villain

00:19:02.440 --> 00:19:03.860 line:80%
with white hair.

00:19:04.040 --> 00:19:06.500 line:80%
Brother-in-Law fought that little villain

00:19:06.550 --> 00:19:08.520 line:80%
and saved my life.

00:19:08.630 --> 00:19:10.110 line:80%
He got hurt.

00:19:10.910 --> 00:19:12.150 line:80%
He got hurt?

00:19:14.350 --> 00:19:15.960 line:80%
Where did you see him?

00:19:16.150 --> 00:19:17.390 line:80%
When did it happen?

00:19:21.350 --> 00:19:22.880 line:80%
Bad people live long lives.

00:19:23.550 --> 00:19:25.070 line:80%
Don't worry, Mrs. Fan.

00:19:25.070 --> 00:19:26.150 line:80%
Yan Zheng wouldn't die easily,

00:19:26.150 --> 00:19:27.950 line:80%
as he can always land on his feet.

00:19:29.110 --> 00:19:31.200 line:80%
Do you know where he is, Mr. Sun?

00:19:34.200 --> 00:19:35.200 line:80%
He...

00:19:37.960 --> 00:19:38.480 line:80%
Hurry!

00:19:38.520 --> 00:19:39.250 line:80%
Come help me!

00:19:39.280 --> 00:19:39.940 line:80%
Grab tight.

00:19:40.280 --> 00:19:40.800 line:80%
Keep up.

00:19:41.770 --> 00:19:42.770 line:80%
Give me a hand.

00:19:44.870 --> 00:19:45.760 line:80%
What happened?

00:19:45.800 --> 00:19:47.860 line:80%
How did these many soldiers get hurt?

00:19:48.150 --> 00:19:48.810 line:80%
Counselor,

00:19:48.830 --> 00:19:50.520 line:80%
a small enemy troop
attempted to storm the mountain.

00:19:50.520 --> 00:19:52.070 line:80%
They fell into our kill zone
and lost half their men.

00:19:52.070 --> 00:19:53.520 line:80%
But many of our fellows got hurt too.

00:19:53.520 --> 00:19:55.240 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an has ordered
the entire army to advance at once.

00:19:55.240 --> 00:19:56.520 line:80%
I got it. I'll be right with him.

00:19:56.520 --> 00:19:57.150 line:80%
Yes!

00:19:57.550 --> 00:19:59.680 line:80%
Mr. Sun, you're a military counselor?

00:20:01.830 --> 00:20:03.150 line:80%
Truth to be told, Mrs. Fan,

00:20:03.150 --> 00:20:04.480 line:80%
"Sun Jin" is just my alias.

00:20:04.480 --> 00:20:06.040 line:80%
My real name is Gongsun Yin.

00:20:06.240 --> 00:20:08.070 line:80%
I'm currently working as
the Xie Army's military counselor.

00:20:08.070 --> 00:20:09.150 line:80%
I'll tell you more later,

00:20:09.150 --> 00:20:10.150 line:80%
as there's an emergency now.

00:20:10.150 --> 00:20:11.040 line:80%
Mr. Gongsun,

00:20:11.720 --> 00:20:13.870 line:80%
I once took care of Yan Zheng
when he was injured.

00:20:13.870 --> 00:20:16.070 line:80%
I can do a good job
cooking herbs and stuff.

00:20:16.070 --> 00:20:17.830 line:80%
Why not let me stay
to attend to the wounded soldiers

00:20:17.830 --> 00:20:18.890 line:80%
as a way to help out?

00:20:21.200 --> 00:20:22.110 line:80%
Not a bad idea.

00:20:22.480 --> 00:20:23.680 line:80%
Do as you see fit then.

00:20:29.320 --> 00:20:29.930 line:80%
Come here.

00:20:31.630 --> 00:20:32.440 line:80%
Changning,

00:20:33.150 --> 00:20:34.830 line:80%
do you know where Yan Zheng is?

00:20:51.110 --> 00:20:52.800 line:80%
Your Lordship is already severely injured,

00:20:52.800 --> 00:20:54.440 line:80%
yet you still handle everything
personally.

00:20:54.440 --> 00:20:56.000 line:80%
On top of that,
the enemy keeps pestering us.

00:20:56.000 --> 00:20:57.590 line:80%
Let me get Your Lordship some anesthetic.

00:20:57.590 --> 00:20:58.440 line:80%
No need.

00:20:58.960 --> 00:21:00.200 line:80%
Save it

00:21:00.200 --> 00:21:01.390 line:80%
for the soldiers.

00:21:01.870 --> 00:21:03.480 line:80%
The sick tent is cramped.

00:21:04.070 --> 00:21:06.440 line:80%
Move some wounded soldiers to my tent.

00:21:06.480 --> 00:21:08.040 line:80%
But will that distract Your Lordship

00:21:08.040 --> 00:21:09.790 line:80%
from addressing military affairs?

00:21:09.790 --> 00:21:10.830 line:80%
Not at all.

00:21:12.150 --> 00:21:14.240 line:80%
Move some lightly wounded soldiers
to this tent.

00:21:14.240 --> 00:21:15.310 line:80%
I won't be affected.

00:21:15.310 --> 00:21:16.480 line:80%
Then use the vacant tents

00:21:16.480 --> 00:21:17.830 line:80%
to house heavily wounded ones.

00:21:17.830 --> 00:21:18.520 line:80%
But...

00:21:19.710 --> 00:21:21.070 line:80%
Just do as I say.

00:21:22.110 --> 00:21:22.720 line:80%
Yes.

00:21:25.520 --> 00:21:27.680 line:80%
Your Lordship, we just finished
interrogating the captives.

00:21:27.680 --> 00:21:28.550 line:80%
They confessed

00:21:28.760 --> 00:21:31.690 line:80%
the enemy army planned to
storm the mountain at dawn.

00:21:32.800 --> 00:21:34.720 line:80%
This isolated mountain is easier to hold
than to take.

00:21:34.720 --> 00:21:35.960 line:80%
Shi Yue is no fool.

00:21:36.930 --> 00:21:38.630 line:80%
He'd never engage in a battle
where he expects

00:21:38.630 --> 00:21:40.520 line:80%
to take more losses than the enemy.

00:21:40.520 --> 00:21:43.240 line:80%
I guess he only meant to
probe my condition

00:21:44.520 --> 00:21:45.800 line:80%
with that small troop,

00:21:46.630 --> 00:21:48.490 line:80%
since I haven't shown up for days.

00:21:57.870 --> 00:21:58.720 line:80%
Then what?

00:21:58.830 --> 00:22:00.910 line:80%
What happened to that little villain?

00:22:00.910 --> 00:22:01.800 line:80%
I don't know.

00:22:01.800 --> 00:22:03.070 line:80%
I've been taken care of

00:22:03.070 --> 00:22:05.520 line:80%
by the counselor
since Brother-in-Law saved me.

00:22:05.520 --> 00:22:06.240 line:80%
Sister,

00:22:06.240 --> 00:22:09.420 line:80%
do you think
Bao'er and Fairy Sister would die?

00:22:09.550 --> 00:22:12.240 line:80%
That big villain's older brother is crazy.

00:22:12.240 --> 00:22:14.480 line:80%
He keeps picking on Fairy Sister.

00:22:14.520 --> 00:22:16.910 line:80%
Bao'er has cried many times in secret.

00:22:17.250 --> 00:22:18.310 line:80%
They wouldn't die.

00:22:18.480 --> 00:22:20.800 line:80%
Auntie Qianqian and Bao'er are very smart.

00:22:20.800 --> 00:22:22.200 line:80%
When we find your brother-in-law,

00:22:22.200 --> 00:22:24.070 line:80%
we'll go down the mountain to rescue them
together.

00:22:24.070 --> 00:22:25.470 line:80%
-How about that?
-Great.

00:22:28.390 --> 00:22:29.440 line:80%
Why are you here?

00:22:32.910 --> 00:22:34.480 line:80%
I had some time to spare, so I thought

00:22:34.480 --> 00:22:35.880 line:80%
I'd come help brew herbs.

00:22:36.040 --> 00:22:38.070 line:80%
All medications in this shed
were personally tasted

00:22:38.070 --> 00:22:40.730 line:80%
and carefully prepared
by the royal physician.

00:22:41.760 --> 00:22:42.800 line:80%
These many?

00:22:43.480 --> 00:22:45.340 line:80%
I had no idea you're heavily sick.

00:22:46.440 --> 00:22:47.570 line:80%
How ignorant of you.

00:22:47.720 --> 00:22:49.870 line:80%
The royal physician tested the medications
on herself

00:22:49.870 --> 00:22:52.600 line:80%
so as to treat the wounded soldiers
effectively.

00:22:52.720 --> 00:22:53.760 line:80%
The army is short on herbs.

00:22:53.760 --> 00:22:55.620 line:80%
We dug these up from the mountain.

00:22:55.830 --> 00:22:56.480 line:80%
Oh right.

00:22:56.800 --> 00:22:59.070 line:80%
You saved my life last time.

00:23:00.400 --> 00:23:02.130 line:80%
Thanks for that. I'm beholden.

00:23:02.390 --> 00:23:03.070 line:80%
No problem.

00:23:03.200 --> 00:23:04.860 line:80%
I don't know your surname yet.

00:23:05.200 --> 00:23:06.070 line:80%
It's "Qi."

00:23:06.390 --> 00:23:07.630 line:80%
"Qi Beholden..."

00:23:08.520 --> 00:23:09.800 line:80%
"Qi Beholden"?

00:23:10.570 --> 00:23:12.030 line:80%
What an interesting name.

00:23:12.280 --> 00:23:12.870 line:80%
You...

00:23:15.680 --> 00:23:18.120 line:80%
Sister, who is she?

00:23:22.120 --> 00:23:24.390 line:80%
Well, she is a royal physician,

00:23:24.440 --> 00:23:25.800 line:80%
who treats the Emperor

00:23:25.800 --> 00:23:27.380 line:80%
in shadow puppet plays.

00:23:29.360 --> 00:23:31.290 line:80%
Nice to meet you, Royal Physician.

00:23:31.520 --> 00:23:32.450 line:80%
Nice to meet you.

00:23:34.260 --> 00:23:36.540 line:80%
This is a battlefield.

00:23:36.910 --> 00:23:38.440 line:80%
Why is your sister here?

00:23:38.830 --> 00:23:41.760 line:80%
My brother-in-law saved my life
and brought me here.

00:23:43.010 --> 00:23:45.250 line:80%
She means my husband, named Yan Zheng.

00:23:47.310 --> 00:23:49.720 line:80%
That explains your determination
to come here.

00:23:49.720 --> 00:23:50.630 line:80%
As it turns out,

00:23:51.440 --> 00:23:53.100 line:80%
you're here for your husband.

00:23:53.870 --> 00:23:55.760 line:80%
I also needed to deliver grain
to the army.

00:23:55.760 --> 00:23:58.390 line:80%
Little did I expect
to reunite with Changning here.

00:23:58.390 --> 00:24:00.280 line:80%
She said my husband was here as well.

00:24:00.280 --> 00:24:01.830 line:80%
But I haven't found him yet

00:24:01.830 --> 00:24:03.440 line:80%
at this huge military camp.

00:24:03.660 --> 00:24:05.630 line:80%
My brother-in-law is rather mighty.

00:24:05.630 --> 00:24:07.870 line:80%
It was he who saved me from bad guys.

00:24:07.910 --> 00:24:11.170 line:80%
He's even better than the generals
in shadow puppet plays.

00:24:11.550 --> 00:24:13.520 line:80%
All those bad guys just collapsed.

00:24:13.960 --> 00:24:16.280 line:80%
Is he even better
than the Marquis of Wu'an?

00:24:16.280 --> 00:24:17.830 line:80%
Yes, he's the best.

00:24:18.200 --> 00:24:21.070 line:80%
She has watched
too many shadow puppet plays.

00:24:21.070 --> 00:24:23.760 line:80%
My husband can't be better
than the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:24:23.760 --> 00:24:25.040 line:80%
If that were true,

00:24:25.070 --> 00:24:27.470 line:80%
he wouldn't have married me,
a pig butcher.

00:24:33.870 --> 00:24:35.270 line:80%
No need to take care of me.

00:24:35.870 --> 00:24:37.330 line:80%
Go attend to the soldiers.

00:24:38.150 --> 00:24:40.080 line:80%
Don't let them know who I really am.

00:24:40.550 --> 00:24:42.630 line:80%
Or they'll feel unease
when they recuperate here.

00:24:42.630 --> 00:24:43.470 line:80%
Understood.

00:24:43.590 --> 00:24:44.650 line:80%
Get some rest then.

00:25:02.220 --> 00:25:04.230 line:80%
[Xie]

00:25:36.680 --> 00:25:37.550 line:80%
Sir,

00:25:38.390 --> 00:25:39.760 line:80%
may I ask what this tent is for?

00:25:39.760 --> 00:25:41.390 line:80%
For soldiers with minor injuries.

00:25:41.390 --> 00:25:43.590 line:80%
So it houses lightly wounded soldiers.

00:25:46.110 --> 00:25:48.030 line:80%
Hello. Is Li Gui here?

00:25:48.050 --> 00:25:49.050 line:80%
In the second bed.

00:25:50.590 --> 00:25:51.850 line:80%
This is your medicine.

00:25:51.930 --> 00:25:52.900 line:80%
Where is Wang Fa?

00:25:53.590 --> 00:25:54.390 line:80%
Here I am.

00:25:56.110 --> 00:25:56.910 line:80%
This is yours.

00:25:57.240 --> 00:25:58.140 line:80%
Thank you.

00:25:58.520 --> 00:25:59.150 line:80%
Zhang Jian?

00:25:59.150 --> 00:26:00.000 line:80%
I'm here.

00:26:00.480 --> 00:26:01.390 line:80%
And this is yours.

00:26:01.390 --> 00:26:03.040 line:80%
You need to take this medicine
two more times.

00:26:03.040 --> 00:26:05.040 line:80%
Once tonight and once tomorrow morning.

00:26:05.040 --> 00:26:06.590 line:80%
Bundle up and get some rest

00:26:06.590 --> 00:26:07.410 line:80%
in the next couple days.

00:26:07.410 --> 00:26:08.110 line:80%
Got it.

00:26:09.850 --> 00:26:11.250 line:80%
Let me check your wounds.

00:26:11.400 --> 00:26:12.650 line:80%
Drink it up.

00:26:26.590 --> 00:26:28.150 line:80%
Go get Physician Beholden now.

00:26:28.150 --> 00:26:29.350 line:80%
This man's wound has opened up.

00:26:29.350 --> 00:26:30.760 line:80%
It needs redressing.

00:26:31.000 --> 00:26:31.680 line:80%
Got it.

00:27:00.150 --> 00:27:01.070 line:80%
Changyu.

00:27:05.280 --> 00:27:06.340 line:80%
Yan Zheng.

00:27:14.420 --> 00:27:15.830 line:80%
I spent a long time looking for you.

00:27:15.830 --> 00:27:16.380 line:80%
Halt!

00:27:23.960 --> 00:27:25.390 line:80%
What are you doing here?

00:27:26.720 --> 00:27:28.200 line:80%
I came here to look for you.

00:27:29.070 --> 00:27:30.600 line:80%
You came here to look for me?

00:27:34.350 --> 00:27:35.950 line:80%
Did the wound reach the bone?

00:27:37.750 --> 00:27:39.280 line:80%
What did the physician say?

00:27:41.150 --> 00:27:42.550 line:80%
It's just a minor injury.

00:27:43.050 --> 00:27:44.850 line:80%
All vital organs are unscathed.

00:27:45.070 --> 00:27:46.470 line:80%
I'll be well in a few days.

00:27:54.000 --> 00:27:55.550 line:80%
It doesn't matter if you're injured

00:27:55.550 --> 00:27:56.910 line:80%
or even disabled.

00:27:58.390 --> 00:27:59.760 line:80%
Stop serving in the army.

00:27:59.760 --> 00:28:01.030 line:80%
Let me take you home.

00:28:01.070 --> 00:28:03.330 line:80%
I can provide for you by butchering pigs.

00:28:09.070 --> 00:28:10.070 line:80%
Little fella,

00:28:10.390 --> 00:28:11.810 line:80%
what a lucky man you are.

00:28:12.080 --> 00:28:14.440 line:80%
Such a pretty girl went to great lengths
to find you.

00:28:14.440 --> 00:28:15.520 line:80%
If I were you,

00:28:15.550 --> 00:28:17.150 line:80%
I could be dead right now

00:28:17.150 --> 00:28:18.280 line:80%
and have no regrets.

00:28:18.910 --> 00:28:19.870 line:80%
Young lady,

00:28:20.000 --> 00:28:22.200 line:80%
I know you care a lot about your husband,

00:28:22.390 --> 00:28:24.000 line:80%
but this is a military camp—

00:28:24.150 --> 00:28:26.390 line:80%
deserters are to be beheaded.

00:28:26.440 --> 00:28:28.640 line:80%
We are Marquis of Wu'an's soldiers now.

00:28:28.830 --> 00:28:30.910 line:80%
If your darling touches the taboo
and gets executed,

00:28:30.910 --> 00:28:32.590 line:80%
where will you find a new husband
as handsome as he is?

00:28:32.590 --> 00:28:33.310 line:80%
Exactly.

00:28:35.040 --> 00:28:37.770 line:80%
This young lady doesn't know the rules,
does she?

00:28:37.800 --> 00:28:39.260 line:80%
She just spoke out of turn.

00:28:39.310 --> 00:28:40.840 line:80%
His Lordship is in the tent.

00:28:40.910 --> 00:28:43.840 line:80%
I'm afraid she has to be punished
under military law.

00:28:43.870 --> 00:28:45.870 line:80%
I wasn't asking you to be a deserter.

00:28:46.070 --> 00:28:48.150 line:80%
I said it wrong, as I was worried sick.

00:28:48.150 --> 00:28:49.410 line:80%
Don't take it to heart.

00:28:50.070 --> 00:28:51.350 line:80%
I know. I understand.

00:28:51.350 --> 00:28:53.460 line:80%
Pass this order quietly:
assemble outside the tent.

00:28:53.460 --> 00:28:56.590 line:80%
-Don't cry.
-Quietly ask everyone to assemble outside.

00:28:57.630 --> 00:28:58.430 line:80%
Counselor...

00:29:02.280 --> 00:29:05.210 line:80%
Pass this order quietly:
assemble outside the tent.

00:29:07.480 --> 00:29:09.280 line:80%
The weather is quite nice today.

00:29:20.720 --> 00:29:21.640 line:80%
There, there.

00:29:21.720 --> 00:29:22.440 line:80%
It's fine.

00:29:23.070 --> 00:29:24.530 line:80%
I know what's on your mind.

00:29:29.150 --> 00:29:29.800 line:80%
Coun...

00:29:34.640 --> 00:29:35.760 line:80%
Is it hurting?

00:29:41.200 --> 00:29:42.330 line:80%
With you by my side,

00:29:43.310 --> 00:29:44.770 line:80%
I don't feel pain anymore.

00:29:56.720 --> 00:29:58.920 line:80%
Where did they go while we were talking?

00:30:00.260 --> 00:30:01.070 line:80%
Let's go.

00:30:01.550 --> 00:30:02.350 line:80%
-Go.
-Go.

00:30:05.240 --> 00:30:06.440 line:80%
I haven't reported to His Lordship

00:30:06.440 --> 00:30:07.960 line:80%
about the fodder for the war horses.

00:30:07.960 --> 00:30:09.150 line:80%
That can wait.

00:30:11.280 --> 00:30:12.820 line:80%
His Lordship enforces
strict military laws.

00:30:12.820 --> 00:30:14.160 line:80%
If I'm late with my report,

00:30:14.160 --> 00:30:15.310 line:80%
I'll be flogged.

00:30:15.800 --> 00:30:17.200 line:80%
You won't, unless you do

00:30:17.440 --> 00:30:18.910 line:80%
intrude on them right now.

00:30:19.760 --> 00:30:20.620 line:80%
Take my advice.

00:30:20.870 --> 00:30:22.390 line:80%
Get in there an hour later.

00:30:23.550 --> 00:30:26.610 line:80%
I am the brilliant counselor
for this entire army.

00:30:29.240 --> 00:30:30.670 line:80%
Would I ever lie to you?

00:30:33.580 --> 00:30:34.380 line:80%
Move!

00:30:36.520 --> 00:30:37.350 line:80%
Changyu!

00:30:39.110 --> 00:30:40.480 line:80%
You found your husband?

00:30:40.910 --> 00:30:42.390 line:80%
I heard he got injured.

00:30:42.870 --> 00:30:44.480 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an is also injured.

00:30:44.480 --> 00:30:46.340 line:80%
I should've checked on him first,

00:30:46.440 --> 00:30:47.760 line:80%
yet I came here instead

00:30:47.870 --> 00:30:49.110 line:80%
to spare you from worries.

00:30:49.110 --> 00:30:50.110 line:80%
Thank you so much.

00:30:50.240 --> 00:30:50.970 line:80%
Come with me.

00:30:54.280 --> 00:30:55.040 line:80%
Yan Zheng.

00:30:55.830 --> 00:30:57.680 line:80%
This is Ms. Qi Beholden,

00:30:58.280 --> 00:30:59.350 line:80%
a beautiful and skilled physician.

00:30:59.350 --> 00:31:00.750 line:80%
I'm sure she can cure you.

00:31:05.440 --> 00:31:07.840 line:80%
So he's the husband
you were talking about?

00:31:08.230 --> 00:31:11.160 line:80%
And she's the military medic
you were talking about?

00:31:14.830 --> 00:31:15.760 line:80%
Anything wrong?

00:31:16.310 --> 00:31:18.170 line:80%
My husband is handsome, isn't he?

00:31:19.260 --> 00:31:20.730 line:80%
You got married?

00:31:22.800 --> 00:31:24.630 line:80%
I didn't see that coming.

00:31:25.480 --> 00:31:26.680 line:80%
You know each other?

00:31:27.740 --> 00:31:30.110 line:80%
Not until just now.

00:31:30.850 --> 00:31:33.040 line:80%
Physician Beholden, please check on him.

00:31:33.040 --> 00:31:33.970 line:80%
No need.

00:31:35.000 --> 00:31:36.730 line:80%
I see you don't trust me, do you?

00:31:40.150 --> 00:31:42.300 line:80%
Although Miss Beholden is young,

00:31:42.960 --> 00:31:44.910 line:80%
she's every serious about her work,

00:31:44.910 --> 00:31:47.510 line:80%
and she treats every patient
wholeheartedly.

00:31:53.760 --> 00:31:55.590 line:80%
Is he really married to you?

00:31:56.000 --> 00:31:57.800 line:80%
Were there betrothal gifts and ceremonies?

00:31:57.800 --> 00:31:59.520 line:80%
Were you tricked by him or what?

00:31:59.520 --> 00:32:00.390 line:80%
Listen,

00:32:00.420 --> 00:32:01.870 line:80%
there are many scammers nowadays.

00:32:01.870 --> 00:32:05.130 line:80%
Some, in particular, have good looks
and sponge off women.

00:32:10.340 --> 00:32:12.130 line:80%
He would never lie to me.

00:32:12.570 --> 00:32:15.030 line:80%
Have you found any internal injuries
in him?

00:32:15.830 --> 00:32:17.520 line:80%
I examined his injuries not long ago,

00:32:17.520 --> 00:32:19.050 line:80%
and found nothing serious.

00:32:19.390 --> 00:32:21.440 line:80%
But due to lack of medicine, meat,

00:32:21.480 --> 00:32:23.280 line:80%
and salt in the army,

00:32:23.910 --> 00:32:25.970 line:80%
his injuries are healing too slowly.

00:32:26.000 --> 00:32:27.370 line:80%
I've been testing medicines recently.

00:32:27.370 --> 00:32:29.650 line:80%
I promise to find the right herbs
for him soon.

00:32:29.650 --> 00:32:30.830 line:80%
Thank you, Beholden.

00:32:30.830 --> 00:32:33.190 line:80%
Didn't you say you had to check on
the Marquis of Wu'an?

00:32:33.190 --> 00:32:34.190 line:80%
You should go now.

00:32:36.390 --> 00:32:39.470 line:80%
I'll leave you to the catching up then,
love birds.

00:32:40.070 --> 00:32:43.650 line:80%
I'm off to visit... the Marquis of Wu'an
now.

00:32:46.830 --> 00:32:47.890 line:80%
Let's go, Jianjia.

00:32:55.980 --> 00:32:57.040 line:80%
Are you alright?

00:32:57.310 --> 00:32:58.440 line:80%
You don't look well.

00:32:59.200 --> 00:32:59.960 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:33:00.760 --> 00:33:02.550 line:80%
Why do you call her "Beholden"?

00:33:03.200 --> 00:33:04.830 line:80%
That royal physician bears
the surname "Qi,"

00:33:04.830 --> 00:33:06.360 line:80%
and given name "Beholden."

00:33:24.060 --> 00:33:25.630 line:80%
The camp lacks all sorts of resources.

00:33:25.630 --> 00:33:27.290 line:80%
There isn't even a decent fan.

00:33:31.590 --> 00:33:32.320 line:80%
Your High...

00:33:32.800 --> 00:33:34.600 line:80%
Royal Physician, I got you a fan.

00:33:41.090 --> 00:33:41.940 line:80%
Isn't this...

00:33:42.830 --> 00:33:44.360 line:80%
Where did you find this fan?

00:33:44.550 --> 00:33:46.390 line:80%
I snatched it from someone.

00:33:46.420 --> 00:33:49.080 line:80%
I was in such a rush
that I didn't see who that was.

00:33:50.310 --> 00:33:51.170 line:80%
Your Highness.

00:33:56.070 --> 00:33:58.020 line:80%
Go and find another fan for me.

00:33:58.040 --> 00:33:58.710 line:80%
Yes.

00:34:09.709 --> 00:34:11.840 line:80%
This humble man greets Your Highness.

00:34:12.280 --> 00:34:14.479 line:80%
Headmaster Gongsun, how have you been?

00:34:15.140 --> 00:34:16.400 line:80%
I've been faring well.

00:34:19.600 --> 00:34:21.310 line:80%
I wonder what brings Your Highness

00:34:21.310 --> 00:34:23.160 line:80%
to this military camp.

00:34:25.760 --> 00:34:28.360 line:80%
-I...
-Your Highness isn't here for me, right?

00:34:28.910 --> 00:34:30.910 line:80%
If Consort Dowager An in the palace knows,

00:34:30.910 --> 00:34:33.110 line:80%
Her Highness will be torn with anxiety.

00:34:35.910 --> 00:34:37.280 line:80%
Headmaster, you're flattering yourself

00:34:37.280 --> 00:34:38.810 line:80%
by making that assumption.

00:34:39.160 --> 00:34:40.630 line:80%
You and the Marquis of Wu'an

00:34:40.630 --> 00:34:43.360 line:80%
came here to quell rebellions
and achieve glory.

00:34:43.560 --> 00:34:44.640 line:80%
Do I, a princess...

00:34:46.200 --> 00:34:47.280 line:80%
a royal physician,

00:34:47.870 --> 00:34:49.240 line:80%
not deserve a bigger stage

00:34:49.240 --> 00:34:51.010 line:80%
than the tiny palace where I'm trapped

00:34:51.010 --> 00:34:53.610 line:80%
and restricted
to meaningless trivialities?

00:34:53.640 --> 00:34:54.830 line:80%
I apologize for my rudeness.

00:34:54.830 --> 00:34:55.950 line:80%
Royal Physician,

00:34:55.950 --> 00:34:57.030 line:80%
I got you a new fan!

00:35:08.350 --> 00:35:10.010 line:80%
Anything else you need to say?

00:35:10.970 --> 00:35:12.120 line:80%
No. I...

00:35:16.910 --> 00:35:18.710 line:80%
This humble man takes his leave.

00:35:30.270 --> 00:35:31.530 line:80%
Let's get back to work.

00:35:46.430 --> 00:35:48.760 line:80%
This tent is for lightly wounded soldiers.
Miss, what are you...

00:35:48.760 --> 00:35:50.070 line:80%
My husband is in there.

00:35:50.270 --> 00:35:53.000 line:80%
-I'll bathe him and change his dressing.
-Leave.

00:35:59.990 --> 00:36:01.000 line:80%
Officers!

00:36:05.240 --> 00:36:06.830 line:80%
Have we met before?

00:36:08.900 --> 00:36:11.240 line:80%
I've traveled far and wide
and seen many people,

00:36:11.240 --> 00:36:12.700 line:80%
but you're not one of them.

00:36:13.340 --> 00:36:15.430 line:80%
You must be mistaken, miss.

00:36:17.200 --> 00:36:17.870 line:80%
Right.

00:36:17.870 --> 00:36:19.560 line:80%
I'm sure you're mistaken.

00:36:19.760 --> 00:36:22.510 line:80%
They're my fellow military men,

00:36:23.200 --> 00:36:24.350 line:80%
Wu and Qi.

00:36:25.430 --> 00:36:26.910 line:80%
I see. You're his brothers-in-arms.

00:36:26.910 --> 00:36:29.030 line:80%
Thank you for taking care of Yan Zheng.

00:36:29.030 --> 00:36:30.180 line:80%
You're welcome.

00:36:30.560 --> 00:36:31.640 line:80%
Well, Yan Zheng,

00:36:31.640 --> 00:36:33.350 line:80%
take a rest and get well soon.

00:36:33.350 --> 00:36:34.580 line:80%
We're heading out now.

00:36:34.580 --> 00:36:35.310 line:80%
Take care.

00:36:55.560 --> 00:36:56.620 line:80%
Bear with the pain.

00:37:36.410 --> 00:37:37.220 line:80%
Is it hurting?

00:37:39.480 --> 00:37:40.270 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:37:45.160 --> 00:37:48.490 line:80%
I should've signed the Divorce Agreement
with you earlier.

00:37:55.870 --> 00:37:57.400 line:80%
Why are you spitting blood?

00:38:00.910 --> 00:38:02.970 line:80%
Are you that desperate to divorce me?

00:38:08.410 --> 00:38:10.290 line:80%
No. I'll never divorce you.

00:38:11.760 --> 00:38:13.220 line:80%
This is what I thought:

00:38:13.720 --> 00:38:15.450 line:80%
you were taken by force to serve

00:38:16.320 --> 00:38:18.680 line:80%
in the army
because you married into my family.

00:38:18.680 --> 00:38:21.340 line:80%
If we had signed the Divorce Agreement
earlier,

00:38:22.280 --> 00:38:24.290 line:80%
you wouldn't have been seized by soldiers

00:38:24.290 --> 00:38:25.850 line:80%
and gotten injured.

00:38:28.560 --> 00:38:30.160 line:80%
Mr. Zhao told me...

00:38:32.230 --> 00:38:33.700 line:80%
to tie up all loose ends

00:38:33.990 --> 00:38:35.350 line:80%
before my last breath.

00:38:36.430 --> 00:38:38.630 line:80%
I already made a decision on my way here:

00:38:40.120 --> 00:38:41.390 line:80%
if I found you alive,

00:38:43.030 --> 00:38:44.450 line:80%
I would take you home;

00:38:45.200 --> 00:38:46.390 line:80%
if I found you dead,

00:38:48.560 --> 00:38:50.020 line:80%
I would collect your body.

00:38:51.140 --> 00:38:52.940 line:80%
During festivals and holidays,

00:38:53.610 --> 00:38:55.430 line:80%
I would burn paper money for you.

00:39:00.840 --> 00:39:02.070 line:80%
I knew it.

00:39:14.830 --> 00:39:16.030 line:80%
I apologize

00:39:17.150 --> 00:39:18.550 line:80%
for what I did that night.

00:39:29.310 --> 00:39:31.040 line:80%
So you do know you did wrong.

00:39:34.760 --> 00:39:37.020 line:80%
I stopped being mad at you
a long time ago.

00:39:41.080 --> 00:39:41.910 line:80%
Jiuheng.

00:39:44.030 --> 00:39:44.720 line:80%
Jiu...

00:39:46.200 --> 00:39:49.400 line:80%
Just a pleasure to meet you again
after so long, Yan Zheng.

00:39:51.500 --> 00:39:54.080 line:80%
I didn't expect you to be here as well,
Mrs. Fan.

00:39:54.080 --> 00:39:54.640 line:80%
Sorry to interrupt.

00:39:54.640 --> 00:39:55.280 line:80%
Go on with your business.

00:39:55.280 --> 00:39:56.030 line:80%
G-Goodbye.

00:39:56.680 --> 00:39:57.470 line:80%
You can stay.

00:39:59.430 --> 00:40:01.360 line:80%
The water is cold. I'll replace it.

00:40:04.970 --> 00:40:06.050 line:80%
I will try to...

00:40:06.640 --> 00:40:07.900 line:80%
bring meat to the army.

00:40:20.080 --> 00:40:21.410 line:80%
It was totally worthwhile

00:40:21.410 --> 00:40:22.950 line:80%
for you to get wounded.

00:40:23.470 --> 00:40:24.310 line:80%
I saw everything.

00:40:24.310 --> 00:40:26.160 line:80%
Mrs. Fan nearly cried her heart out.

00:40:26.160 --> 00:40:26.870 line:80%
And you...

00:40:27.200 --> 00:40:28.380 line:80%
Get off.

00:40:38.990 --> 00:40:39.690 line:80%
I'm here for a serious matter.

00:40:39.690 --> 00:40:40.350 line:80%
Speak up.

00:40:42.830 --> 00:40:44.280 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing attempted

00:40:44.680 --> 00:40:45.560 line:80%
to threaten you

00:40:45.560 --> 00:40:47.720 line:80%
with Mrs. Fan's little sister.

00:40:48.330 --> 00:40:50.390 line:80%
If word about Mrs. Fan

00:40:50.510 --> 00:40:52.510 line:80%
reaches Prime Minister Wei's ears,

00:40:53.800 --> 00:40:55.400 line:80%
given his usual practice...

00:40:55.470 --> 00:40:57.130 line:80%
you know what he's capable of.

00:40:58.910 --> 00:41:00.350 line:80%
Keep all of today's events

00:41:00.350 --> 00:41:01.430 line:80%
secret.

00:41:02.240 --> 00:41:03.900 line:80%
Do not disclose a single word.

00:41:05.800 --> 00:41:08.260 line:80%
The Xie family's guards
all have tight lips.

00:41:08.390 --> 00:41:09.830 line:80%
The soldiers on the front line

00:41:09.830 --> 00:41:11.760 line:80%
don't even know what you look like.

00:41:12.560 --> 00:41:13.830 line:80%
But they are aware

00:41:13.950 --> 00:41:18.430 line:80%
that Mrs. Fan found her missing husband
in the camp.

00:41:21.390 --> 00:41:22.560 line:80%
I think...

00:41:23.350 --> 00:41:25.280 line:80%
I'd better stay in a separate tent.

00:41:25.950 --> 00:41:26.990 line:80%
Just in case.

00:41:30.200 --> 00:41:33.080 line:80%
In case your real identity is revealed,
or in case you want to

00:41:33.080 --> 00:41:34.610 line:80%
get intimate with Mrs. Fan?

00:41:37.200 --> 00:41:38.660 line:80%
Let's talk real business.

00:41:38.830 --> 00:41:41.240 line:80%
When exactly will you tell her the truth?

00:41:45.200 --> 00:41:48.000 line:80%
I'll explain everything to her
at the proper time.

00:41:49.430 --> 00:41:51.230 line:80%
This young woman risked her life

00:41:51.830 --> 00:41:54.230 line:80%
to look for her husband
on the battlefield.

00:41:54.640 --> 00:41:56.390 line:80%
Given such loyalty and devotion,

00:41:56.390 --> 00:41:57.510 line:80%
she deserves the truth.